{{See|tío}}

==Esperanto==
===Pronunciation===
*[[International Phonetic Alphabet|IPA]] /ˈti.o/

===Etymology===
Esperanto demonstrative [[:Category:Esperanto correlatives|correlative]] prefix ''[[ti-]]'' + object correlative suffix ''[[-o]]''

===Pronoun===
'''tio'''

#[[that]], that thing.
#: As with other demonstrative correlatives in Esperanto, prefixing ''[[tio]]'' with ''[[ĉi]]'' produces the proximal version of the word, so Esperanto ''ĉi tio'' means English ''this [thing]''.

